<cb:div>
<pb n="0066a" xml:id="I01.0026.0066a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0066a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 26</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0066a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>蔣伯仙造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0066a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0066a0101">大魏孝昌三年歲次乙未九月<note n="0066001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30506"/>＝辛【史】</note><note n="0066001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30506"/>【佛拓】，辛【史】</note><app n="0066001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">辛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30506"/></rdg></app>酉朔十日
<lb ed="I" n="0066a02" type="honorific"/>庚午。司州東郡東燕人蔣伯<note n="0066002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠇈＝仙【史】</note><note n="0066002" resp="ihp" type="mod">𠇈【佛拓】，仙【史】</note><app n="0066002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">仙</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠇈</rdg></app>。敬造彌勒石像
<lb ed="I" n="0066a03" type="honorific"/>一區。清寧天宮。一時俱就。瞻仰嘆曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0066a04" type="honorific"/>夫真覺無言。非演說無以詮其旨。應<note n="0066003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30361"/>＝雖【史】</note><note n="0066003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30361"/>【佛拓】，雖【史】</note><app n="0066003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">雖</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30361"/></rdg></app>隨感。非
<lb ed="I" n="0066a05" type="honorific"/>真容無以標其見。故捨苦<note n="0066004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠕀＝罔【史】</note><note n="0066004" resp="ihp" type="mod">𠕀【佛拓】，罔【史】</note><app n="0066004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">罔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠕀</rdg></app>若歸心於真應。脩
<lb ed="I" n="0066a06" type="honorific"/>善莫若精崇於經像。寔以半偈獲投身之感。剋
<lb ed="I" n="0066a07" type="honorific"/>朝皆成道無疑。如斯微漸。由建解脫於此岸之
<lb ed="I" n="0066a08" type="honorific"/>下。會無為於彼岸之上。況乃洪<note n="0066005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30508"/>＝遘【史】</note><note n="0066005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30508"/>【佛拓】，遘【史】</note><app n="0066005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遘</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30508"/></rdg></app><note n="0066006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30509"/>＝顯【史】</note><note n="0066006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30509"/>【佛拓】，顯【史】</note><app n="0066006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30509"/></rdg></app>於大千。麗
<lb ed="I" n="0066a09" type="honorific"/>造<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">鮮</unclear>於涌塔。茲速出生死於煩<note n="0066007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">惚＝惱【史】</note><note n="0066007" resp="ihp" type="mod">惚【佛拓】，惱【史】</note><app n="0066007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">惱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">惚</rdg></app>之<note n="0066008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">渕＝淵【史】</note><note n="0066008" resp="ihp" type="mod">渕【佛拓】，淵【史】</note><app n="0066008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">淵</lem><rdg wit="【原】">渕</rdg></app>。駿入常
<lb ed="I" n="0066a10" type="honorific"/>樂於我淨之境。自非人通四果。行齊十地。誰能
<lb ed="I" n="0066a11" type="honorific"/>捨此家珍。崇此奇造也。故佛弟子蔣伯仙。可謂
<lb ed="I" n="0066a12" type="honorific"/>望挺台岳之標。智通解行之首。結<note n="0066009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𩔊＝願【史】</note><note n="0066009" resp="ihp" type="mod">𩔊【佛拓】，願【史】</note><app n="0066009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">願</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𩔊</rdg></app>崇福。咸脩
<lb ed="I" n="0066a13" type="honorific"/>來善。庶令道齊塵沙。惠充一切。竭己　良粢。造
<lb ed="I" n="0066a14" type="honorific"/>石像一區。光夫一丈。起子之年。功成　乙未之
<lb ed="I" n="0066a15" type="honorific"/>末。志力欣齊。應成<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">等</unclear>日。但基廣<note n="0066010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30512"/>＝營【史】</note><note n="0066010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30512"/>【佛拓】，營【史】</note><app n="0066010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">營</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30512"/></rdg></app>高。徐而弗促。
<lb ed="I" n="0066a16" type="honorific"/>尒乃功妙奚方。羨同梵巧。神匠演思。資奇□□
<lb ed="I" n="0066a17" type="honorific"/>冥感。鏤玉錭文。鐫真顏於妙相。明如瑠璃。光□
<lb ed="I" n="0066a18" type="honorific"/>景月。准辰定而置華宇。臨萇湖而□□原。□□
<lb ed="I" n="0066a19" type="honorific"/>紫微勢本<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">洍</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">長</unclear>其尊容□□□□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0066a20" type="honorific"/>宮殿葦曄。若寶塔□□□□□□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0066a21" type="honorific"/>見閻浮祇洹。聖造重顯於今日。觀其□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0066a22" type="honorific"/>二義之堅。越於五春之茂。僉矚斯妙。□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0066a23" type="honorific"/>述<note n="0066011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30513"/>＝敷【史】</note><note n="0066011" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30513"/>【佛拓】，敷【史】</note><app n="0066011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">敷</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30513"/></rdg></app>愚思於<app type="star" corresp="#0066010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">營</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30512"/></rdg></app>素。勒扶於□石。敬<note n="0066012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30514"/>＝圖【史】</note><note n="0066012" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30514"/>【佛拓】，圖【史】</note><app n="0066012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30514"/></rdg></app>□□□□。
<lb ed="I" n="0066a24" type="honorific"/>靡惙不能適照。景<app type="star" corresp="#0066005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遘</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30508"/></rdg></app>聊述万一。　　其詞曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0066a25" type="honorific"/>妙哉正覺。應化迦毗。降魔鹿菀。万<note n="0066013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𧉾＝蠢【史】</note><note n="0066013" resp="ihp" type="mod">𧉾【佛拓】，蠢【史】</note><app n="0066013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蠢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧉾</rdg></app>咸歸。廣濟
<lb ed="I" n="0066a26" type="honorific"/>度訖。雙林漸暉。眾生咸嘆。幽惠湌<note n="0066014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30515"/>＝啓【史】</note><note n="0066014" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30515"/>【佛拓】，啓【史】</note><app n="0066014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">啓</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30515"/></rdg></app>。嗚吁慈父。
<lb ed="I" n="0066a27" type="honorific"/>有類何往。等為懷情。鐫石<app type="star" corresp="#0066012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30514"/></rdg></app>像。不有尊儀。<note n="0066015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30517"/>＝孰【史】</note><note n="0066015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30517"/>【佛拓】，孰【史】</note><app n="0066015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">孰</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30517"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0066a28" type="honorific"/>遵孰仰。<note place="inline">其一</note>尊<note n="0066016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30518"/>＝顏【史】</note><note n="0066016" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30518"/>【佛拓】，顏【史】</note><app n="0066016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顏</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30518"/></rdg></app>奇特。鏤玉錭文。明淨瑠璃。灼□
<lb ed="I" n="0066a29" type="honorific"/>炳分。如月無霄。如日無雲。王宮載生。耆闍□
<lb ed="I" n="0066a30" type="honorific"/>欣。<note place="inline">其二</note>宮像葦曄。卜要而安。臨湖<note n="0066017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢴃＝據【史】</note><note n="0066017" resp="ihp" type="mod">𢴃【佛拓】，據【史】</note><app n="0066017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">據</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢴃</rdg></app>原。清信<note n="0066018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𥪰＝競【史】</note><note n="0066018" resp="ihp" type="mod">𥪰【佛拓】，競【史】</note><app n="0066018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">競</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𥪰</rdg></app>歡。
<lb ed="I" n="0066a31" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">罕</unclear>遇覆載。妙齊祇洹。緣茲善被。万<app type="star" corresp="#0066013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蠢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧉾</rdg></app>同歡。
<lb ed="I" n="0066a32" type="honorific"/>像出梨山。　凡用功三千日。</p>
